	<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-7 col-md-8 col-lg-9">
	<p>A Labrador Retriever or simply Labrador is one of the most popular breeds in the world, a dog of kings and presidents, stars and ordinary servants, blind and disabled people, policemen and rescuers. The list of celebrities who have Labradors is very long: the English Queen and the American President, French President, Prince Charles, the royal family of Monaco, the Rothschild family, Charles Aznavour, Nikolai Karachentsev, Joe Dassin ...</p>
